    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……mihoさん、お疲れ様です\nfranさん達とだいぶ激しくやり合ったみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あの……mihoさん、お疲れ様です\nfranさん達とだいぶ激しくやり合ったみたいですね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……その、差し入れを持ってきたので\nmihoさんも休憩して、お一ついかがですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……その、差し入れを持ってきたので\nmihoさんも休憩して、お一ついかがですか……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで怯えなくても結構ですよ、失礼ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そこまで怯えなくても結構ですよ、失礼ですね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8417230924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……あの子達とやり合ったと言いますか\n件のカバー曲の練習を、始めたはいいものの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はぁ……あの子達とやり合ったと言いますか\n件のカバー曲の練習を、始めたはいいものの",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3083892505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "改めて曲を聴き返して、プランも練ったはずなのに\nfranとkanaに歌わせるとイメージと違うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "改めて曲を聴き返して、プランも練ったはずなのに\nfranとkanaに歌わせるとイメージと違うんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1083892505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、調整を繰り返していたら\n二人して怒鳴り始めて……で、さっきの有り様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それで、調整を繰り返していたら\n二人して怒鳴り始めて……で、さっきの有り様です",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6750559171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "二人が気に食わないと暴れるのはいつものことですし\nそれはまぁ、どうでもいいのですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "二人が気に食わないと暴れるのはいつものことですし\nそれはまぁ、どうでもいいのですけど",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6083892505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、少しは気にしてあげて下さい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いや、少しは気にしてあげて下さい……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8750559171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "曲のカバーを持ちかけたfranさんはともかく\nkanaさんは付き合ってくれてるだけですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "曲のカバーを持ちかけたfranさんはともかく\nkanaさんは付き合ってくれてるだけですし……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.366666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "カバー曲のお披露目イベントはすでに決まっていますし\nそれまでに、曲をちゃんと仕上げなければいけないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "カバー曲のお披露目イベントはすでに決まっていますし\nそれまでに、曲をちゃんと仕上げなければいけないのに",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "これでは、カバーで昔を思い出してもらうどころか\nいらぬ炎上を招くだけだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "これでは、カバーで昔を思い出してもらうどころか\nいらぬ炎上を招くだけだわ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.566666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁまぁ……少し休んで、頭を冷やしましょう\n今はまだfranさん達も落ち着かないでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ま、まぁまぁ……少し休んで、頭を冷やしましょう\n今はまだfranさん達も落ち着かないでしょうし",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "別に、私は冷静ですけど\n今すぐあの子達を引きずり戻すのは不可能ですしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "別に、私は冷静ですけど\n今すぐあの子達を引きずり戻すのは不可能ですしね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8275049528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "そう言えばさっき、差し入れがあると言っていましたね\nせっかくですし、一ついただきましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そう言えばさっき、差し入れがあると言っていましたね\nせっかくですし、一ついただきましょうか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.8999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どうぞ\nこころ達が番組の収録でもらってきたらしいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はい、どうぞ\nこころ達が番組の収録でもらってきたらしいんですけど",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7999994914,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
